articles.title: Human ancestors were near extinction some 900,000 years ago, says study - FRANCE 24 English
articles.description: A study published on Thursday claims that human ancestors teetered on the brink of extinction over 900,000 years ago. Based on a new method of analysis, scientists found that our ancestors survived in a group of less than 1,300 individuals.
